Milestone Description:
- Basic chaining notation in place 
- System to read what is available in the set of constructors

This is a milestone to change the signature of constructors to return a partial transformation, or partial measurement, instead of a transformation or measurement as we currently do. Partial transformations/partial measurements are functions that take an input domain and input metric, and return a transformation or measurement.

For a full explanation, see #664
Used retrospectively to see issues completed per quarter (or other time period) related to maintenance/performance--indirectly related to functionality initiatives.
